{{Infobox company | name = Eskew+Dumez+Ripple | location = [[New Orleans]], [[Louisiana]] | key_people = Allen Eskew, Steven Dumez, and Mark Ripple | industry = [[Architecture]] | num_employees = 40+ | homepage = [http://www.eskewdumezripple.com/ Eskew+Dumez+Ripple Official Website] | caption = Design excellence. Environmental responsibility. Community outreach. Client commitment. }} ''' Eskew+Dumez+Ripple''' is an American architecture practice based in [[New Orleans]], [[Louisiana]] founded by Allen Eskew, Steven Dumez and Mark Ripple.
