{{Infobox artwork/wikidata|year=1894|location=[[Rijksmuseum]]}} '''''Two Girls in the Snow''''' is an 1894 oil on canvas painting by the Dutch artist [[Isaac Israels]]. It was bought from the artist in 1904 for the private Drake-Fraser collection in London, which lent it to the [[Rijksmuseum]] in Amsterdam in 1917. It was then bought by the museum in 1944.
